devdoc.details: Manages APY adjustments based on loan characteristics such as amount and duration.

params.durationSeconds: The duration of the loan in seconds.

returns._0: uint256 Calculated APY in basis points.

params._baseAPY: The new base APY in basis points.

params._factor: The new duration bonus factor in basis points per year.

params._rates: Array of risk premiums corresponding to the thresholds.

@title AdvancedAPYManager
 @dev Manages APY adjustments based on loan characteristics such as amount and duration.
@notice Initializes the contract with the lending token.
